ATTRIBUTION & DERIVATIVE-WORK NOTICE
------------------------------------

Fluers is a native Rust reimplementation of the architecture of Flue,
"The sandbox agent framework", created by Fred K. Schott and the Astro
team:

    Upstream project : Flue — https://github.com/withastro/flue
    Original author  : Fred K. Schott  (https://github.com/FredKSchott)
    Organization     : Astro (https://astro.build)
    Upstream license : Apache License, Version 2.0

Fluers re-implements Flue's architecture from first principles in Rust.
It is not a line-by-line translation of the TypeScript source. All design
credit for the agent-harness architecture belongs to Fred K. Schott and
the Astro contributors. See NOTICE for the full derivative-work notice
required by Apache-2.0 §4.
